data.description: The "Woodcrest", a large Front to Back Split plan by Elevate Design + Build, with an amazing covered front porch. Great room has vaulted ceiling with wood beams, & fireplace feature wall. Open Kitchen with large island and built in table, granite counters, walk-in pantry, beautiful wood floors, and buffet counter/zoom desk with butcher block top and floating shelves above. Master bedroom has a shiplap feature wall and large walk-in closet. Master bathroom has a floating double vanity & amazing shower. Finished basement with rec room & 1/2 bath. Unfinished sub-basement for storage. Extra deep 3 car garage has room for all your toys.
